                            <div class="choose-card-content">
                                <h2>Every detail in the grip of your hands.</h2>
                                <p>We aim to provide details about places to eat, activities, and places to visit around the city.
                                  Users can refer to the website for such detais.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="choose-us-card" id="choose-3">
                            <div class="card-icon">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-mountain-sun"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="choose-card-content">
                                <h2>Truested to all users Worldwide</h2>
                                <p>Our website, even though neew to the market, is loved and truested by costumers that have used 
                                  the website.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="choose-us-card" id="choose-4">
                            <div class="card-icon">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="choose-card-content">
                                <h2>Created by Team Nexa, so it's a Win</h2>
                                <p>We aim in expaninding the website to cover more touristy cities like Chandigadh, Delhi, Manali,
                                  Ladakh, etc to provide users with more features and details about places all over India.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

        <footer>
            <div class="footer-container">
                <div class="social-icons">
                   <a href=""><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i></a>
